OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy overnight, but with a few
OL,7,Fbreaks in the cloud here and there.
OL,8,FSome showery outbreaks or rain and
OL,9,Fdrizzle are possible, especially over
OL,10,Fhigher ground.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many with
OL,13,Fpatchy drizzle, mostly in the west.
OL,14,FHowever the cloud will lift and break
OL,15,Fup readily with sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. A strengthening
OL,17,Fsouthwesterly wind later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
